	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There isn't much that can't be a form of expression or emotion; especially coming from a human.
<br />
<br />Someone could fart while curling their pinky finger, hop, and drink a glass of water to make art.
<br />
<br />Someone could program 2 gigabytes worth of code that does absolutely nothing for artistic expression.
<br />
<br />It depends on the person and the use of the code.  Inherently not all programming or code is art, but it could be if the author intended or someone else classified it as art.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


